			<tr>
				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=1162">Neriak</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Kizdean Gix</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Kizdean Gix</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=3159"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:">Keorg</a> | 
		                        9/2/1999 3:07:51 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">   You must talk to the man at the top of the Lodge of the Dead and ask him about courier duties. He will then hand you a note with a list of current runners. One of them is Kizdean Gix. You can find him in the West Commonlands and must ask him about messages for Neriak. Reward is a few copper, faction changes, and some items.
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
